Create a new repository on GitHub
Launch GitBash
    cd Desktop
    mkdir basic_repo
    touch index.html
    touch style.css
    git init
    git add .
    git commit -m 'first commit'
    git remote add origin https://github.com/taylor-fancher/basic_repo.git
    git push -u origin master
    git add .
    git commit -m 'minor changes'
    git push -u origin master